==English==
===Etymology===
From Middle Dutch [[boecweite]] or Middle Low German [[bokwete|bōkwēte]] ‘beech-wheat’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈbʌkwi:t/}}

===Noun===
'''buckwheat'''

# an [[Asian]] [[plant]], of the [[species]] ''[[Fagopyrum esculentum]]''
# the [[fruit]] of this plant used as a [[cereal]]

